ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectP.C. 2010-497 of April 22, 2010 ** AMENDMENT **
PrecisOrder Amending Order in Council P.C. 2010-497 of April 22, 2010, in order to replace “986.648 hectares (2,437.97 acres)” by “984.603 hectares (2,433.03 acres)” for the setting apart of lands for the use and benefit of BINGWI NEYAASHI ANISHINAABEK for a new reserve, identified as Sand Point First Nation Reserve, in Ontario, reducing the total by 2.045 hectares (4.94 acres).
